main event: Two white circular objects were observed in the sky side by side, one above the other, appearing the size of a golf ball.
interesting points: The sighting was reported by Boeing Aircraft Company,The objects emitted a slight whine sound,The objects passed through an opening and light faded upon being covered by a hatch,The observation lasted for approximately 2 minutes, and they were moving in a northward direction.
sighted object: two white circular objects in the sky
